1 hundred thousand dollars ($600,000) in nonrecurring funds to be allocated to the North Carolina
2 Collaboratory to conduct the evaluation and report described in this section.
3
4 PART VII. EFFECTIVE DATE
5 SECTION 7. Except as otherwise provided, this act becomes effective July 1, 2026.
